$lang['Just like in decimal, after 16 symbols have been used in Hexadecimal, the order of numbers starts over again at zero. So, hexadecimal 10 is equal to decimal 16, and hexadecimal 11 is equal to decimal 17. And so on!'] = 'Pērā i te ā-ira, i muri i te whakamahi tohu 16 ki te Hexadecimal, ka timata ano te raupapa tau ki te kore. Na, ko te hautekauono 10 he rite ki te ira-a-ira 16, ko te hautekauono 11 he rite ki te ira-a-ira 17. A pera tonu!';
